OL,4,CCovid-19: No singing inside schools
OL,5,Cafter Easter break
OL,6, Schools have been told that no singing
OL,7, can take place indoors when pupils
OL,8, return after the Easter break.
OL,10,FThe instruction from Education Minister
OL,11,FPeter Weir prohibits pupils singing
OL,12,Findividually or in choirs.
OL,14,FHowever, pupils will be allowed to sing
OL,15,Foutside alone or in choirs as long as
OL,16,Fthey are socially distanced.
OL,18,FMr Weir said the decision had been
OL,19,Ftaken on the advice of the chief
OL,20,Fmedical officer and the Public Health
OL,21,FAgency (PHA).
